<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Golang on Cyrus' Blog</title><link>https://Cyrus-iwnl.github.io/categories/golang/</link><description>Recent content in Golang on Cyrus' Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 22 Apr 2025 17:20:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://Cyrus-iwnl.github.io/categories/golang/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Golang 学习日记 Day2</title><link>https://Cyrus-iwnl.github.io/p/golang-%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E6%97%A5%E8%AE%B0-day2/</link><pubDate>Tue, 22 Apr 2025 17:20:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://Cyrus-iwnl.github.io/p/golang-%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E6%97%A5%E8%AE%B0-day2/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://Cyrus-iwnl.github.io/p/golang-%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E6%97%A5%E8%AE%B0-day2/go.jpg" alt="Featured image of post Golang 学习日记 Day2" /></description></item><item><title>Golang 学习日记 Day1</title><link>https://Cyrus-iwnl.github.io/p/golang-%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E6%97%A5%E8%AE%B0-day1/</link><pubDate>Tue, 22 Apr 2025 16:43:16 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://Cyrus-iwnl.github.io/p/golang-%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E6%97%A5%E8%AE%B0-day1/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://Cyrus-iwnl.github.io/p/golang-%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E6%97%A5%E8%AE%B0-day1/go.jpg" alt="Featured image of post Golang 学习日记 Day1" />&lt;h2 id="包变量与函数">&lt;a href="#%e5%8c%85%e5%8f%98%e9%87%8f%e4%b8%8e%e5%87%bd%e6%95%b0" class="header-anchor">&lt;/a>包、变量与函数
&lt;/h2>&lt;h3 id="包package">&lt;a href="#%e5%8c%85package" class="header-anchor">&lt;/a>包（Package）
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>Go 程序由包组成。每个 Go 源文件都需要以 package 声明开头。常见的 main 包表示可独立运行的程序，其入口为 main() 函数。&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="导入import">&lt;a href="#%e5%af%bc%e5%85%a5import" class="header-anchor">&lt;/a>导入（Import）
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>通过 import 关键字导入其他包，例如：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-go" data-lang="go">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kn">import&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;fmt&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="导出名exported-name">&lt;a href="#%e5%af%bc%e5%87%ba%e5%90%8dexported-name" class="header-anchor">&lt;/a>导出名（Exported Name）
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>在 Go 中，以大写字母开头的标识符是可导出的（即公有），小写开头的则是私有的。&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="函数function">&lt;a href="#%e5%87%bd%e6%95%b0function" class="header-anchor">&lt;/a>函数（Function）
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>函数使用 func 关键字定义，例如：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-go" data-lang="go">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kd">func&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nf">add&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">a&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kt">int&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">b&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kt">int&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kt">int&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="k">return&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">a&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">+&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">b&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="多返回值">&lt;a href="#%e5%a4%9a%e8%bf%94%e5%9b%9e%e5%80%bc" class="header-anchor">&lt;/a>多返回值
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>Go 支持一个函数返回多个值：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-go" data-lang="go">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kd">func&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nf">swap&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">x&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">y&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kt">string&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kt">string&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kt">string&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="k">return&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">y&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">x&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="带名字的返回值">&lt;a href="#%e5%b8%a6%e5%90%8d%e5%ad%97%e7%9a%84%e8%bf%94%e5%9b%9e%e5%80%bc" class="header-anchor">&lt;/a>带名字的返回值
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>返回值可以具名：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-go" data-lang="go">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kd">func&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nf">split&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">sum&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kt">int&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">x&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">y&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kt">int&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">x&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">sum&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">*&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">4&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">/&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">9&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">y&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">sum&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">-&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">x&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="k">return&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="变量">&lt;a href="#%e5%8f%98%e9%87%8f" class="header-anchor">&lt;/a>变量
&lt;/h2>&lt;h3 id="声明变量">&lt;a href="#%e5%a3%b0%e6%98%8e%e5%8f%98%e9%87%8f" class="header-anchor">&lt;/a>声明变量
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>使用 var 声明变量：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-go" data-lang="go">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kd">var&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">i&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kt">int&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="初始化变量">&lt;a href="#%e5%88%9d%e5%a7%8b%e5%8c%96%e5%8f%98%e9%87%8f" class="header-anchor">&lt;/a>初始化变量
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>可以同时声明并初始化：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-go" data-lang="go">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kd">var&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">j&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kt">int&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">1&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="短变量声明">&lt;a href="#%e7%9f%ad%e5%8f%98%e9%87%8f%e5%a3%b0%e6%98%8e" class="header-anchor">&lt;/a>短变量声明
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>函数内部可以使用更简洁的 := 方式：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-go" data-lang="go">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nx">k&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">:=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">3&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="基本类型">&lt;a href="#%e5%9f%ba%e6%9c%ac%e7%b1%bb%e5%9e%8b" class="header-anchor">&lt;/a>基本类型
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>Go 提供诸如 int, float64, bool, string 等基本类型。&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="零值">&lt;a href="#%e9%9b%b6%e5%80%bc" class="header-anchor">&lt;/a>零值
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>未显式初始化的变量会被赋予“零值”。&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="类型转换与类型推断">&lt;a href="#%e7%b1%bb%e5%9e%8b%e8%bd%ac%e6%8d%a2%e4%b8%8e%e7%b1%bb%e5%9e%8b%e6%8e%a8%e6%96%ad" class="header-anchor">&lt;/a>类型转换与类型推断
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>Go 不支持隐式类型转换，必须显式转换：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-go" data-lang="go">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kd">var&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">i&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kt">int&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">42&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kd">var&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">f&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kt">float64&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nb">float64&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">i&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>Go 具有类型推断能力：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-go" data-lang="go">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nx">v&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">:=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">42&lt;/span> &lt;span class="c1">// 推断为 int 类型&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="常量">&lt;a href="#%e5%b8%b8%e9%87%8f" class="header-anchor">&lt;/a>常量
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>使用 const 定义常量：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-go" data-lang="go">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kd">const&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">Pi&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mf">3.14&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="控制结构">&lt;a href="#%e6%8e%a7%e5%88%b6%e7%bb%93%e6%9e%84" class="header-anchor">&lt;/a>控制结构
&lt;/h2>&lt;h3 id="for-循环">&lt;a href="#for-%e5%be%aa%e7%8e%af" class="header-anchor">&lt;/a>for 循环
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>Go 仅有一种循环结构：for。&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-go" data-lang="go">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="k">for&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">i&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">:=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">0&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">i&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">10&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">i&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">++&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">fmt&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nf">Println&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">i&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h4 id="无限循环">&lt;a href="#%e6%97%a0%e9%99%90%e5%be%aa%e7%8e%af" class="header-anchor">&lt;/a>无限循环
&lt;/h4>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-go" data-lang="go">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="k">for&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="c1">// ...&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h4 id="for-是-go-中的-while">&lt;a href="#for-%e6%98%af-go-%e4%b8%ad%e7%9a%84-while" class="header-anchor">&lt;/a>for 是 Go 中的 while
&lt;/h4>&lt;p>可用 for 模拟 while：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-go" data-lang="go">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="k">for&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">condition&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="c1">// ...&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="条件语句">&lt;a href="#%e6%9d%a1%e4%bb%b6%e8%af%ad%e5%8f%a5" class="header-anchor">&lt;/a>条件语句
&lt;/h3>&lt;h4 id="if-判断">&lt;a href="#if-%e5%88%a4%e6%96%ad" class="header-anchor">&lt;/a>if 判断
&lt;/h4>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-go" data-lang="go">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="k">if&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">x&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">0&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">x&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">-&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">x&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h4 id="if-与简短语句">&lt;a href="#if-%e4%b8%8e%e7%ae%80%e7%9f%ad%e8%af%ad%e5%8f%a5" class="header-anchor">&lt;/a>if 与简短语句
&lt;/h4>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
